description:
Non-material minor amendment of planning permission ref: P05245 dated 06/07/2007.  The non-material minor amendments are:
A]        reconfiguration of the internal layout of residential dwellings and service apartments at all levels (residential habitable rooms remain unchanged at 283hr and serviced apartment unit numbers remain unchanged at 72);
B]        reconfiguration of circulation spaces at all levels including relocation of lift/stair cores, together with amended/new entrances at ground floor; 
C]        reconfiguration of the basement level layout, together with relocation of refuse/recycling enclosures to basement level;
D]        covering of ground floor internal courtyard and inclusion of glazed rooflights at first floor level; 
E]        reconfiguration of the layout of business accommodation; and
F]	the creation of a new condition listing the approved drawing numbers.
